data.title: Module:Location map/data/Spain Province of Santa Cruz de Tenerife
data.text:
Location map of Province of Santa Cruz de Tenerife name Province of Santa Cruz de Tenerife border

coordinates 28.939107 -18.273066 ←↕→ -15.996487 27.553078 map center image Santa Cruz de Tenerife-loc.svg

Module:Location map/data/Spain Province of Santa Cruz de Tenerife is a location map definition used to overlay markers and labels on an equirectangular projection map of Province of Santa Cruz de Tenerife. The markers are placed by latitude and longitude coordinates on the default map or a similar map image.

Usage

These definitions are used by the following templates when invoked with parameter "Spain Province of Santa Cruz de Tenerife":

{{Location map|Spain Province of Santa Cruz de Tenerife |...}}

{{Location map many|Spain Province of Santa Cruz de Tenerife |...}}

{{Location map+|Spain Province of Santa Cruz de Tenerife |...}}

{{Location map~|Spain Province of Santa Cruz de Tenerife |...}}

Map definition

name = Province of Santa Cruz de Tenerife

Name used in the default map caption

image = Santa Cruz de Tenerife-loc.svg

The default map image, without "Image:" or "File:"

top = 28.939107

Latitude at top edge of map, in decimal degrees

bottom = 27.553078

Latitude at bottom edge of map, in decimal degrees

left = -18.273066

Longitude at left edge of map, in decimal degrees

right = -15.996487

Longitude at right edge of map, in decimal degrees

Precision

Longitude: from West to East this map definition covers 2.2766 degrees.

At an image width of 200 pixels, that is 0.0114 degrees per pixel.

At an image width of 1000 pixels, that is 0.0023 degrees per pixel.

Latitude: from North to South this map definition covers 1.386 degrees.

At an image height of 200 pixels, that is 0.0069 degrees per pixel.

At an image height of 1000 pixels, that is 0.0014 degrees per pixel.

See also

Module:Location map/data/Canary Islands

Module:Location map/data/Spain

Location map templates

Template:Location map, to display one mark and label using latitude and longitude

Template:Location map many, to display up to nine marks and labels

Template:Location map+, to display an unlimited number of marks and labels
